 \int_{T/4}^0 \frac{4t}{T}~dt-\int_{T/4}^{T/2} \frac{4t}{T}~dt\\ 
\begin{align*}\int\limits_{T/4}^0\frac{4t}Tdt&=\left.\frac2Tt^2\right|_{T/4}^0=-\frac2T\frac{T^2}{16}=-\frac T8\\\int\limits_{T/2}^{T/4}\frac{4t}Tdt&=\left.\frac2Tt^2\right|_{T/2}^{T/4}=\frac2T\left(\frac{T^2}{16}-\frac{T^2}4\right)=-\frac{3T}8\end{align*}
 \int_{T/4}^0 - \int_{T/4}^{T/2} \quad = \quad \int_{T/4}^0 + \int^{T/4}_{T/2} \quad = \quad \int_{T/2}^0 
 \int_a^b+\int_b^c=\int_a^c. 
